{
  "texts": [
    "Authors in [141] proposed VAE-CaCE to overcome TCAV's limitations.TCAV has a significant difficulty distinguishing between confounding features such as 'car' and 'bicycle' that are very similar.",
    "The causal effect of higher-level features is considered in VAE-CaCE to quantify the importance of concept for model decision.",
    "Work in [162] proposed DISSECT, a robust generative method for determining the importance score and efficiently distinguishing concepts with high similarities.",
    "The authors applied the Concept Traversals Sequences method to a challenging malignant and benign skin dataset.",
    "Work in [160] recently proposed CAR (Concept Activation Region) to extend the CAV [69] idea and propose an accurate explanation of confounding concepts."
  ]
}